{"tid":1251110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於621行動有失民意","createTime":"2019-06-22T11:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T11:57:56.000Z","uid":175123,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4e780861a59afb4848aa0ba59a9fbdf645e8f1b0","tid":1251110,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"屌你文宣部好心唔好再話我地前線失民意然後叫我地收手，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本文宣個宣傳對象唔應該係前線/勇武派，而係公眾</span><br />\n<br />\n覺得我地失民意嘅話，就應該靠你地去贏返民心。文宣再阻止有用而肯付出嘅義士真係會好打擊士氣，想為場抗爭出力就應該教育返公眾掟雞蛋真係冇任何損傷，而且亦都係表達激進派意見嘅最溫和嘅手段。"},{"pid":"9543bacbc179635a3663f08a19f847a8b28d9719","tid":1251110,"uid":175123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539af7da19018f933fd2e16d84e0c7ec31663e53","tid":1251110,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a4d28d565c7343ac1c9bde2237409f90954bd1","tid":1251110,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91d5cf6a590547164eb36175cb9afff00b6be5d","tid":1251110,"uid":58041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"邊個話621有失民意<br />\n我好敬佩成件事喎"},{"pid":"c71515dbd1c25e8c31efae1f9605f41e9611f725","tid":1251110,"uid":139883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"建議大家唔好再入/回覆一d同自己持相反意見既Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上面係超級好用既意見"},{"pid":"ebb9b075c74de228d680efbe22aef9120ef89388","tid":1251110,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"互相配合啦"},{"pid":"